main event: A sighting of a UFO resembling a baseball was reported over Newfoundland on April 9, 1960.
interesting points: The sighting occurred between 1900 and 2300Z,The object was seen moving in an arc on a southeastern course,Another similar object was observed to the north shortly after this sighting,The length of observation was approximately half an hour,It was suggested that the object might have been a meteor.
